OL,3,CFormer footballer Joey Barton denies
OL,4,Cassault outside golf club
OL,6,FFormer footballer Joey Barton has
OL,7,Fdenied seriously injuring a man in an
OL,8,Falleged assault outside a golf club.
OL,10,FBarton, 43, who is accused of assault
OL,11,Foccasioning grievous bodily harm,
OL,12,Fappeared at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,13,Faccused of attacking Kevin Lynch at
OL,14,FFairway, Huyton, on 8 March.
OL,16,FThe former Manchester City footballer,
OL,17,Ffrom Widnes, Cheshire, who wore a grey
OL,18,Fzip-up fleece and with glasses on,
OL,19,Fappeared via videolink from HMP
OL,20,FLiverpool for the plea hearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
