OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775578269
OL,3,CFormer footballer Joey Barton denies
OL,4,Cassault outside golf club
OL,6,FBarton's co-defendant Gary O'Grady,
OL,7,F50, of Huyton, Merseyside, was not
OL,8,Fasked to enter a plea to the charge.
OL,10,FBoth will now face a seven-day trial
OL,11,Fon 1 September.
OL,13,FAn earlier court hearing was told the
OL,14,Fdefendants had been drinking with Mr
OL,15,FLynch at Huyton and Prescot Golf Club
OL,16,Fbefore the alleged attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
