PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1775578269
OL,3,CFormer footballer Joey Barton denies
OL,4,Cassault outside golf club
OL,6,FMr Lynch, a former non-league football
OL,7,Fmanager and founder of special
OL,8,Feducation school NexGen Academy, was
OL,9,Fsaid to have suffered serious injuries
OL,10,Fto his eye.
OL,12,FThe 15-minute hearing also dealt with
OL,13,Fadministrative matters.
OL,15,FBarton was remanded in custody, while
OL,16,Fthe judge renewed conditional bail for
OL,17,FO'Grady, who was supported in court by
OL,18,Fseveral family members.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
