OL,3,CFormer footballer Joey Barton denies
OL,4,Cassault outside golf club
OL,6,FFormer Manchester City and QPR
OL,7,Fmidfielder Barton has one England cap
OL,8,Fand also played for Newcastle,
OL,9,FRangers, Burnley and Marseille.
